Upgrade the system with advanced analytics and prepare for enterprise-level authentication.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - We will install **MSAL** libraries for the authentication scaffold.
> - A feature flag `VITE_USE_AUTH` will be used to control the authentication requirement.
> - The backend will now provide CSV streaming for reports.

